{
  "stem": "9730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- the-- there's a German proverb that goes something like, the appetite grows with the eating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So he at least admitted that much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was just one of the experiences along the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After Metz, we-- we finally, you know-- and after those forts surrendered, we finally were able to push on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we actually crossed into Germany, so far still on-- on the-- on the west side of-- of the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But then we-- we got to the Rhine in-- in March of '45 and were able to cross it in a town called Nierstein.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And from then on, things developed pretty rapidly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But of course, at first, there was still, in the winter of-- of '44, '45 was, of course, the Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "At that time we were in Alsace-Lorraine, the Third Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when the Germans went on the offensive, we were called as reinforcements and accomplished that move in-- really in record time, and to bolster our defenses against the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And fortunately, were able to stem their advance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when-- once the weather cleared and our Air Force could start their bombings and strafings, of course it became a lot better.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we stopped the Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then, as I said, from there we went to Germany, at first to the rural area, a town called Iserlohn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then we also advanced on the-- on the city of Frankfurt, and-- and we took that city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And later on, you know, we crossed-- we crossed such-- before then, we crossed such well-known places as Bitburg, for instance, and-- until we came to the Rhine and crossed it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And our main objective then became Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
